{"tid":1748212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有事搵立法會證員求助，係點樣搵佢地？","createTime":"2019-11-23T14:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:01:09.000Z","uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec238ace4763ef740ba247407027dccf075ad1e","tid":1748212,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"其實係有關近數月抗爭運動既事，我有事想搵某d立法會議員求助。<br />\n我諗比較合適既係，毛孟靜、朱凱迪呢d<br />\n我試過搵毛姨姨，例如跟佢立法會議員個contact去搵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/members/yr16-20/mc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fmembers%2Fyr16-20%2Fmc.htm&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FtOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=33ad321a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/members/yr16-20/mc.htm</a><br />\n亦試過去佢Facebook sent message。無回音。我估，其實呢d公開既聯終方法，可能有好多人港共人士拿來玩滋優，所以實際上未必通。<br />\n<br />\n所以上黎問各位，如何搵到佢地，我有事求助   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1eeb7988853f5af752dfcb9075263690b505c8","tid":1748212,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d3ade595253f5920bb1f4b703c8e6489d413da9c","tid":1748212,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"求指教呀！！！    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb29d578bce716314a87215b530ea737b615c303","tid":1748212,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"議員辦事處?"},{"pid":"d686cc3fb948e540c3a0bdb007ad9fd40ab904d6","tid":1748212,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb29d578bce716314a87215b530ea737b615c303","tid":1748212,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"議員辦事處?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:10:10.000Z","msg":"咦？聽你咁講，我就上網試下查毛孟靜議員辦事處，結果發現，原來佢有個辦事處位於何文田邨恬文樓 (但詳細地址不明)。呢